"Small codes and large image databases for recognition," Computer
Vision and Pattern Recognition, 2008. CVPR 2008. IEEE Conference on , vol.,
no., pp.1,8, 23-28 June 2008<o:p class=3D""></o:p></span></p><p class=3D"Ms=
oNormal">[4] Norouzi, M.; Punjani,
